      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it. It\u2019s been so reliable for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs beautifully and has been super well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. If you're looking for a solid, great-looking ride that won't let you down, this is the one. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
