    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example has been properly maintained for performance longevity, with the critical 'Big Three' addressed: rear subframe reinforcement has been completed, the VANOS system is serviced, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a limited-slip differential that provides excellent lock-up under load. While the paint exhibits minor road rash consistent with its mileage, the individual throttle bodies offer instantaneous response and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A true driver\u2019s car with robust mechanicals and a solid service history.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
