      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the seating surfaces are firm and free of rips, and every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a consistent service history that ensures peace of mind. It drives straight and true, with a firm suspension and responsive braking. This is a turn-key car that offers a premium experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
